      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "RE: Unidentified Flying Object,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "Torrington, Conn.,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "5 December 1957",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "Dear Sir:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "Inclosed is a copy of a letter from a Delmaine H. Oveson, who",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "identifies himself as Director of Operations, Electronics Service",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "Unit 4, Roseau, Minnesota. This letter requests information concern-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "ing the reported sighting of an Unconvential Aerial Object on or about",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "5 December 1957 at Torrington, Connecticut.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "This letter was furnished the Office of Special Investigations",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "by the Ground Observer Corps (GOC) Coordinator for the State of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "Connecticut. That individual has advised that an alleged sighting",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "of an unidentified flying object near Torrington, Connecticut, was",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "reported on or about 5 December 1957, but that neither he nor the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "addressee have any knowledge of the author of the inclosed letter.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "Information has been received from the U. S. Army, and Air Force",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "Postal Service that no military units are located at Roseau, Minnesota.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "Therefore, this matter is being referred to your Bureau for any action",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "you deem appropriate.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "Advice if any information of interest to the Air Force is",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "developed by your Bureau in this matter will be appreciated.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "status": "blank"
    },
